race.comment: IMASTATEMENT (7) is yet to break through after six career starts. Fitter now with the claim after fading late when fifth over 1000m at this track. Value chance. BLACK NATURE (5) was doing her best work late on debut here 12 days ago. Is sure to have come on from that but will likely get back again from the draw. Watch for her launching late again. MANAPOURI (3) didn't threaten fresh but had excuses. Gets weight relief with the claimer engaged. Don't give up on him yet. LONG TIME LOVERS (9) was below her best last time, finishing ninth over 1300m at Narromine after being in the firing line on the turn. Back in class and assess on earlier efforts.
